members.name: MediaStreamTrackEvent()
members.description: Constructs a new MediaStreamTrackEvent with the specified configuration.

parameters.name: type
parameters.description: A DOMString representing the name of the type of the MediaStreamTrackEvent. It is case-sensitive and can be "addtrack" or "removetrack".

parameters.name: track
parameters.description: A MediaStreamTrack object representing the track which was added to or removed from the stream.
